snippet.title: Antichamber - Teaser Trailer
snippet.description:
Take a look at the colorful, twisting world of the new indie game in this psychedelic trailer for Antichamber, where FPS standards go to die. Antichamber will be released for PC / Mac in 2012.

Head over to IGN for more awesome indie game coverage:
http://pc.ign.com/

Subscribe to IGN's channel for reviews, guides, trailers and all things gaming: http://www.youtube.com/subscription_center?add_user=ignentertainment
